    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DISCORD</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A DAY IN SPACE</h2> 。<br><br><strong>在 &quot;太空殖民地 &quot;上进行太空探险，这是一个高科技的空间站，在2040年被派往新发现的欧米茄星球进行殖民。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698400/extras/583b8ea9b0022d997e59f495e92a2364.avif?t=1629734567\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong><br>在这个互动的空间探索体验中，你将。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 探索巨大的 &quot;太空殖民地一号 &quot;空间站。<br></li><li> 执行你的日常任务。<br></li><li> 与你的船员互动，了解他们的个人故事。<br></li><li> 了解人类首次太空殖民的原因。<br></li><li> 收集所有的线索，找出你的同伴死亡背后令人震惊的真相。</li></ul></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698400/extras/03a118847115fbffe6a80418686f8f59.poster.avif?t=1629734567\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698400/extras/03a118847115fbffe6a80418686f8f59.webm?t=1629734567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698400/extras/03a118847115fbffe6a80418686f8f59.mp4?t=1629734567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
